            "options": "<div class='alert alert-info'><h5>How to get an API key:</h5><ul><li><b>Anthropic (Recommended):</b> Go to <a href='https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys' target='_blank'>console.anthropic.com</a> → API Keys → Create Key. Uses Claude Sonnet by default. Reliable, no rate-limit issues.</li><li><b>OpenRouter (Free tier):</b> Sign up at <a href='https://openrouter.ai' target='_blank'>openrouter.ai</a> → Keys. Free models available but may be rate-limited.</li><li><b>Groq:</b> Sign up at <a href='https://console.groq.com' target='_blank'>console.groq.com</a> → API Keys. <em>May not work from cloud-hosted servers.</em></li><li><b>HuggingFace:</b> <a href='https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens' target='_blank'>huggingface.co</a> → Access Tokens.</li></ul></div>"
